when they arrested me.

26:45.272 --> 26:47.691
About Leo Newman.

26:50.277 --> 26:53.530
After the college investigation found
no evidence of wrongdoing,

26:53.614 --> 26:54.865
I said I let it go.

26:57.201 --> 26:58.410
But I didn't. Iâ€¦

26:59.912 --> 27:06.126
I thought it must be a cover-up,
so I started a sort of-- a campaign.

27:07.753 --> 27:10.756
Pretended to be other people online,
planted rumors on message boards,

27:10.839 --> 27:13.383
made accusations
about why Leo had got his place.

27:14.968 --> 27:16.845
Then I got a phone call.

27:17.846 --> 27:21.350
I was told if I carried on
smearing Leo Newman and his family,

27:21.433 --> 27:23.268
not only would it cost me my job,

27:23.352 --> 27:25.354
but my reputation would also be destroyed

27:25.437 --> 27:28.232
and I'd lose everything,
including my family.

27:28.315 --> 27:30.526
I was still married then. Soâ€¦

27:32.194 --> 27:33.362
What did you do?

27:35.697 --> 27:38.492
I said, "Fuck you.
How dare you threaten me?"

27:38.575 --> 27:40.577
I was more careful, but I carried on.

27:44.540 --> 27:46.416
Then one day my husband called

27:46.500 --> 27:49.127
to say the school phoned him
while I was in a lecture.

27:52.422 --> 27:55.217
Someone had picked Daisy up
from music practice,

27:55.300 --> 27:57.302
pretending to know me, andâ€¦

28:00.806 --> 28:02.224
and taken her.

28:07.980 --> 28:10.732
We called the police.
I've never been so scared in my life.

28:12.192 --> 28:14.194
Even more than tonight. It wasâ€¦

28:19.741 --> 28:21.952
A few hours later, I got another call.

28:22.953 --> 28:24.246
Saying what?

28:24.329 --> 28:25.914
Where to pick up the kid.

28:27.457 --> 28:30.043
That she'd had a lovely time,
been bought sweets and fizzy drinks,

28:30.127 --> 28:32.171
but don't doubt how serious we are.

28:32.254 --> 28:33.505
Forget about Leo Newman.

28:33.589 --> 28:36.383
Now, not to spoil the ending,
but it'll be light soon.

28:36.466 --> 28:39.636
The guy who phoned with the first warning,
did you get his name?

28:39.720 --> 28:41.930
-How did you know what they said?
-It's classic.

28:42.514 --> 28:44.641
You've done that to people.

28:44.725 --> 28:47.644
You only meet someone like me
if you ignore that one.

28:47.728 --> 28:51.773
I don't get it.
Why won't you tell NCA the whole story?

28:54.818 --> 28:57.696
They were already trying
to say I had a grudge against the Newmans.

28:57.779 --> 28:59.281
It would have made me look more guilty.

28:59.364 --> 29:01.408
But you do have a grudge
against the Newmans.

29:01.491 --> 29:03.118
Yeah, me and a million others.

29:16.089 --> 29:21.094
I took this off the guy
who was sent to kill me.

29:21.178 --> 29:23.472
And he's dead now, isn't he?

29:24.097 --> 29:25.557
If we could get into thisâ€¦

29:34.399 --> 29:35.776
You need a password.

29:40.948 --> 29:42.866
Okay. Okay.

29:43.867 --> 29:46.870
You got something personal of his,
like a phone?

29:47.538 --> 29:48.747
Yeah. I've been through it.

29:50.874 --> 29:53.043
There's nothing
that looks like a password.

29:54.044 --> 29:56.672
That's 'cause
it's not his regular password.

29:56.755 --> 29:59.716
-It's a boot log-in.
-What's that?

29:59.800 --> 30:01.635
Gets you into the BIOS.

30:13.772 --> 30:15.607
Told you I'm not a carpet salesman.

30:18.819 --> 30:20.070
Where's his email?

30:24.950 --> 30:26.118
Empty.

30:27.578 --> 30:31.748
Empty-- Petraeus. Petraeus. Petraeus.

30:35.711 --> 30:39.339
Whoever he was,
he's been emailing someone at CNPR.

30:39.423 --> 30:40.591
How do you know?

30:40.674 --> 30:42.759
Because this stock template was
in the server

30:42.843 --> 30:44.553
they obviously didn't want anyone
to know about.

30:44.636 --> 30:47.431
And if you stop talking for a minute,
I'll tell you more.

30:50.392 --> 30:51.935
-"M. Copeland."
-Who's that?

30:52.769 --> 30:56.398
It's Martin Copeland. He is the COOâ€¦

30:57.816 --> 30:59.902
